		<h1>Further simplification</h1>
		<p>Our recent studies showed that the level of BIM proficiency and the years using BIM strongly correlate with the level of BIM adoption and the level of BIM implementation. Based on this finding, the number of the slim BIM indices was further reduced to two as shown in Table 3:</p>

		`
		<div class="panel panel-default">
                        <div class="panel-heading">
                            Table 3. slim BIM indices - Set 2
